                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240715-21-off112 t18240715-21-crimeloc115"></join>; my handkerchief was in my right hand coat pocket. I stood to let two persons pass, and felt a touch at my pocket, turned round, and seeing the prisoner near me I charged him with it - he denied it, but afterwards produced my handkerchief.</p>





